Simple:
templates > post_list.html:
	limit preview size
templates > post_edit.html
templates > post_list.html:
	show when latest change - if changed since publish
Read up on forms(ex. form.as_p, form.as_ul etc.)


Advanced:
Startapp('Syndication')
Publish RSS feed of latest posts

Startapp('RSSReader')
Display RSS Feed
Extra: Change displayed RSS feed?

Questions:
References to methods are written in lowercase, but the method starts with a capital letter